                    <locus target="#126r" facs="128">Fol. 126r</locus>
                    <desc>
                    ink pen trial
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e4">
                    <locus from="1r" to="12r" facs="003">Fols 1r–12r, </locus><locus from="12v" to="17v" facs="015">12v–17v</locus>
                    <desc>
                    The manuscript contains small numbers in the margin, about every tenth line. In the case of 1r–12r they are the number 10. From 12v–17v, the number is 80
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e5">
                    <locus target="#26 #42" facs="028 044">Fols. 26, 42</locus>
                    <desc>
                    yellow yarn is sewn into the fore edge to mark content as navigation system;
                    </desc>
                    </item>
