                    <locus target="#31 #51 #73r #105r" facs="005 007 075 107">Fols. 31, 51, 73r, 105r</locus>
                    <desc>
                    red yarn is sewn into the fore edge to mark content as navigation system
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e7">
                    <locus target="#5r #15v #36v #50v #62r" facs="007 018 039 053 064">Fols. 5r, 15v, 36v, 50v, 62r</locus>
                    <desc>etc., words of text are written interlinearly
