                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e8">
                    <locus target="#84v" facs="087"> f. 84v line 3</locus>
                    <desc>
                    words of text are written in the upper margin with a symbol (┴) marking the location where the text is to be inserted
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e9">
                    <locus target="#19v #43r #46r #49v" facs="022 045 048 052">Fols. 19v, 43r, 46r, 49v</locus>
                    <desc>etc., erasure markings are visible
